<p>Document recovered from Location of Interest within Temecula, California after Operation &quot;Delivery Service&quot; that was previously owned by the Ambrose Restaurant. This document is preserved for use by MTF Lambda-14 (&quot;One Star Reviewers&quot;) in their continuing efforts to combat this group of interest.</p>
