<p><em><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Customer Reviews:</span> Temecula</em></p>
</div>
<blockquote>
<div style="text-align: right;">
<p><span style="font-size:150%;">@AirConditionedLaurie<br />
★★★★☆</span></p>
</div>
<br />
Great place to eat with a good selection of food!
<p>Good to finally have a place to eat that suits my more esoteric tastes. Great location too!<br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></p>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<div style="text-align: right;">
<p><span style="font-size:150%;">@Quarterporter<br />
★★★★☆</span></p>
</div>
<br />
I've spent a couple of enjoyable evenings here, the changing menu items are interesting, but I feel like using actual self-modifying menus would improve it a lot.<br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></blockquote>
<blockquote>
<div style="text-align: right;">
<p><span style="font-size:150%;">@fredazx1fn0q2rc<br />
★★★☆☆</span></p>
