<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></blockquote>
<blockquote>
<div style="text-align: right;">
<p><span style="font-size:150%;">@ready-to-freddie<br />
★★★★★</span></p>
</div>
<br />
The atmosphere is really down to earth, which is tricky to pull off with some of these menu items! Five stars!<br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></blockquote>
<blockquote>
<div style="text-align: right;">
<p><span style="font-size:150%;">@emptyjudith<br />
★★☆☆☆</span></p>
</div>
<br />
