<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></blockquote>
<blockquote>
<div style="text-align: right;">
<p><span style="font-size:150%;">@morecircularhome<br />
★★★☆☆</span></p>
</div>
<br />
Place was crawling with guards, I think there was some kind of incident recently? Managed to have an enjoyable enough meal, but I was constantly on edge.<br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></blockquote>
<blockquote>
<div style="text-align: right;">
<p><span style="font-size:150%;">@alarming_julius<br />
★☆☆☆☆</span></p>
</div>
<br />
